234
00:19:41,330 --> 00:19:44,500
Estou de volta!

235
00:19:45,370 --> 00:19:49,380
– Capitão Buggy! – Capitão Buggy!

236
00:19:51,420 --> 00:19:54,090
Desculpe por ter demorado tanto, homens!

237
00:19:55,420 --> 00:19:59,430
Hora de animar as coisas com uma Buggy Ball super chamativa!

238
00:20:08,730 --> 00:20:10,520
